---
title: Easy Indian Lamb & Veggie Curry with Basmati Rice
description: A curry in only 25 minutes? With our easy four-step recipe, you'll have a delicious dish ready in a jiffy and with the help of bright Mumbai spices, it'll be looking like the deep golden rays of the sunset. Who needs riches when you have this silky, rich coconut curry instead?
